you look like a condom.\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You do.\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2026 You put that poncho right around your head and tied it like a little balloon.\\\"\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Kotb's snap, she smiled for the camera in her poncho while standing next to Cruise, who appeared wet from the rainy weather.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Do you know when you dream of meeting Tom Cruise \\u2026 And then it finally happens,\\\" she wrote alongside her July 26 Instagram upload.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Though Kotb explained that she wore the poncho to protect her clothes and hair in the event she had to go on air during the event, Bush Hager continued to poke fun at her post's caption.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"score\": 0.9999999987398951, \"rank\": 1.2461197969023537e-09, \"text\": \"Bush\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The best part is she's like, 'I have always dreamed of meeting him.'\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I just wonder, honestly, in her dream, did she have a shower cap on?\\\"\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1100, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"she teased.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bush Hager also compared Kotb's poncho look to photos of her father, former PresidentGeorge W. Bush,struggling with his ponchoatDonald Trump's 2017 presidential inauguration.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1114, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"score\": 0.9999999987398951, \"rank\": 1.2461197969023537e-09, \"text\": \"Bush\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\"}, {\"begin\": 1209, \"end\": 1213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"score\": 0.9999999987398951, \"rank\": 1.2461197969023537e-09, \"text\": \"Bush\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\"}, {\"begin\": 1249, \"end\": 1254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999454303, \"rank\": 5.066771126914122e-11, \"text\": \"Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am like, 'You are my dad!\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are my dad!'\\\"\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"she joked.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Later onHoda & Jenna, Bush Hager showed a side-by-side of Kotb and her dad's poncho pics, stating, \\\"I mean, tell me you all are not separated at birth.\\\"\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"score\": 0.9999999987398951, \"rank\": 1.2461197969023537e-09, \"text\": \"Bush\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bush Hager has previously made hilarious comparisons between her cohost and her father, re