her\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Father\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Dad says put the vodka down.'\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2085, \"end\": 2088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Father\", \"score\": 0.6823796992865416, \"rank\": 0.4654597068012809, \"text\": \"Dad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Father\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Father\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But guess what?\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dad wasn't out the night we got here.\\\"\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Adding to the pair's connection, Bush Hager teamed up with her dad to create a heartfelt birthday present for Kotb.\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"score\": 0.9999999987398951, \"rank\": 1.2461197969023537e-09, \"text\": \"Bush\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had my dad, who has started painting, paint your favorite photo of you holding your girls,\\\" Bush Hager said on the Kotb's 60th birthday celebration episode ofHoda & Jennaon Monday, August 12.\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2382, \"end\": 2386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"score\": 0.9999999987398951, \"rank\": 1.2461197969023537e-09, \"text\": \"Bush\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The picture - which featured Kotb walking alongsideher daughtersHaley, 7, and Hope, 5 - brought both women to tears.\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2598, \"entitie